summary: The diff implements all four requirements comprehensively. REQ-1 is satisfied by presetSongs.ts with 15 songs across three categories using the existing Note type. REQ-2 is satisfied by SongLibraryDialog.tsx integrated into MusicEditor.tsx. REQ-3 is satisfied by GuidedPlaybackView.tsx and useGuidedPlayback.ts with all required controls. REQ-4 is satisfied by NoteSequenceGuide.tsx with scrolling, highlighting, dimming, and mini hole diagrams. All acceptance criteria appear to be met.
